OL,4,CCovid-19 pandemic: Italy to shut shops
OL,5,Cand schools amid infection spike
OL,6, Shops, restaurants and schools will be
OL,7, closed across most of Italy on Monday,
OL,8, with PM Mario Draghi warning of a "new
OL,9, wave" of the coronavirus outbreak.
OL,11,FFor three days over Easter, 3-5 April,
OL,12,Fthere will be a total shutdown.
OL,14,FItaly, which one year ago imposed one
OL,15,Fof the first national lockdowns, is
OL,16,Fonce again struggling to contain the
OL,17,Frapid spread of infections.
OL,19,FThe country has reported more than
OL,20,F100,000 Covid-related deaths, Europe's
OL,21,Fsecond-highest tally after the UK.
